{"tid":1302468,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB大股東係共產黨黨員黎瑞剛，你地仲對TVB有期望？","createTime":"2019-07-10T03:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T07:09:54.000Z","uid":14503,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31b563290d234141e4e47d6003554a6442518c9e","tid":1302468,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"仲同TVB傾訴求有用咩？<br />\n根本真係CCTVB黎！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n2017年5月，香港證監會經調查TVB的一項商業回購計劃後，質疑「中國梅鐸」黎瑞剛是TVB實際大股東，更猜測其背後另有「話事人」。證監會表示，集團現時最大單一股東「Young Lion Holdings」，涉及不同股權架構，因此要求TVB交代大股東股權架構全部詳情。消息稱TVB拒絕就範，不排除就此司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/黎瑞剛\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%BB%8E%E7%91%9E%E5%89%9B&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8Ck5YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=a294e32c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/黎瑞剛</a>"},{"pid":"3a367bc04e98dea5094a4be1a13b227830d3411d","tid":1302468,"uid":14503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:11:08.000Z","msg":"黎瑞剛（1969年－），籍貫上海，生於甘肅省蘭州市，是中華人民共和國傳媒人，中國共產黨黨員，曾任上海廣播電視台台長、上海文廣新聞傳媒集團總裁、中共上海市委副秘書長和市委辦公廳主任。目前是華人文化產業投資基金董事長，現任香港電視廣播有限公司董事局副主席兼非執行董事，邵氏兄弟控股董事局主席及非執行董事。"},{"pid":"552f7c202e427cb32ac4e68ec9ad8fcad1340144","tid":1302468,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:11:33.000Z","msg":"文宣部請出手"},{"pid":"817fd66a4b1da56e9e73e6865cfa3effebac85a3","tid":1302468,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:11:49.000Z","msg":"比多d人知"},{"pid":"0088489574aed62b041a71df130e0da063dc45bc","tid":1302468,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f0c699bee1bb4dd6e8112268a77323573e7c17f","tid":1302468,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T03:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img sr